          <description><span style="background-color:#CDFF7D;border-bottom:2px groove #000000;font-style:italic;">Submitter: Thermokon Sensortechnik GmbH</span><br/><br/><span style="border-bottom:2px groove #000000;">Data exchange</span><br/>Direction: bidirectional (Smart-Ack)
              <br/>Addressing: broadcast and addressed
